Submit an employment intermediary report
This page is also available in Welsh (Cymraeg).

chunks.html_content: You’ll need a Government Gateway user ID and password. If you do not have one, you can create one when you submit a report.
chunks.plain_content:
Submit an employment intermediary report
You’ll need a Government Gateway user ID and password. If you do not have one, you can create one when you submit a report.

chunks.html_content: You must upload a report every 3 months. You may be charged a penalty if your report is late, incomplete or incorrect.
